## üéØ QUICK REFERENCE GUIDES

### Financial Ratios Quick Reference
| Ratio | Formula | Good Range | Purpose |
|-------|---------|------------|---------|
| Current Ratio | Current Assets / Current Liabilities | 1.5-3.0 | Liquidity |
| Quick Ratio | (Current Assets - Inventory) / Current Liabilities | 1.0-2.0 | Immediate liquidity |
| Debt-to-Equity | Total Debt / Total Equity | <0.5 | Leverage |
| ROE | Net Income / Shareholders' Equity | >15% | Profitability |
| ROA | Net Income / Total Assets | >5% | Asset efficiency |
| Gross Margin | (Revenue - COGS) / Revenue | >30% | Profitability |

